channel.title: Need a modeller?
channel.description:
Does anybody need a modeller for custom items or something. I can make knives, spears shields, pretty much anything you want. I have a little experience in java, JavaScript and c#. I am quite new to moddeling and I want to get better, you can only get better with practise. I am not great at texturing but with rsps you don't need fancy textures :)
Sorry if this is wrong section, I wasn't sure if I am to post in general or here. So move if inappropriate section. This is one of the first models I made in blender. See it here http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,549620.0.html
Thanks for reading, my Skype is ben.heath118 if you need me
